{"tid":941438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【星島煙仔何】獨立關稅區　美商會：唔想取消　特首就要多多訪美","createTime":"2018-12-14T18:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T19:21:57.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4abd22af6a87c7dafd2b8bb9784b5e900a444acc","tid":941438,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1925074-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%92%A4%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8C%E9%81%99%E9%81%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1925074-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2581%2599%25E9%2581%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E3%2580%258D&d=op9W95%2Bgdyoq%2FZPxI5W7hbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=16b06355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1925074-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2581%2599%25E9%2581%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E3%2580%258D&h=b8d05191\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1925074-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%92%A4%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8C%E9%81%99%E9%81%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/12/10/460543/i_350x255_408533835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F12%2F10%2F460543%2Fi_350x255_408533835.jpg&h=04547297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（星島日報報道）美國國會「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」，上月在報告中提議取消香港獨立關稅區地位，引起各界擔憂。香港美國商會會長早泰娜（Tara Joseph）接受本報專訪，認為香港不必過分擔心。但她指出，更應該關注事件背後反映「香港在美國政商界中的存在感正在消失」，呼籲香港特首以及高層官員多訪問美國。<br />\n<br />\n「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」上月在其年度報告中指出，「中國當局一直違反讓香港高度自治的承諾」，建議國會重新審視《美國－香港政策法》中香港享有的獨立關稅區的地位，以調整美國對香港出口科技產品的策略。<br />\n<br />\n「這件事情不應當簡單化」，她說，應該從幾個方面去看待，一方面說明撰寫報告的委員會不夠了解香港；另一方面，香港也不夠積極地在海外推廣自己享有的獨特地位。「今年我去了四次華盛頓，我們在美國聽到的反饋是，香港在美國不夠積極，發聲不強。香港特首已經很久沒有去美國了。」<br />\n<br />\n今年九月商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華訪美，以及立法會議員赴美游說，早泰娜表示讚許，「親自到場（showing up）是很重要的。我們非常鼓勵香港官員多多訪美，參與建設性對話。」"},{"pid":"a990e68fb26b7fcd1f9b5ead99373bf4463f412f","tid":941438,"uid":103981,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"當年董曾去美國係見總統，而家隨時市長都唔知有無得見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81083c451583d7a5a1c3716bfecb1a6555104174","tid":941438,"uid":21035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T19:20:59.000Z","msg":"根本就想香港地位消失<br />\n<br />\n曾生以前見總統都係同佢平排咁一左一右，大家咁高咁大<br />\n<br />\n而家689/777見果陣成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b43381be7ccacb69557c98691b193d38e85fdbd","tid":941438,"uid":21035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就想香港地位消失<br />\n<br />\n曾生以前見總統都係同佢平排咁一左一右，大家咁高咁大<br />\n<br />\n而家689/777見<span style=\"color: red;\">雜總</span>果陣成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}